        <p>At Sample Website, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information.</p>

        <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We may collect personal information, including but not limited to your name, email address, and phone number, when you use our services.</p>

