        <p>We take security measures to protect your personal information. Your data is stored securely, and we follow industry standards for data protection.</p>

        <h3>Cookies</h3>
        <p>Our website may use cookies to enhance your experience. You can review our <a href="#">Cookie Policy</a> for more details.</p>

        <h3>Changes and Updates</h3>
        <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time, so please check the last update date.</p>

        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions or feedback regarding privacy, please visit our <a href="#">Contact Us</a> page.</p>
    </div>
